title: Desktop non lite interface issues with Approve and/or stake button
body: Does anyone else have issues Staking when using the regular Sushi Bar interface? I have tried from several browsers using windows and wallet methods to be clicking the stake button without anything popping up. If you find this issue to be true vote yes for a proposal to make an update fix (:
